{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "06", "m": "07", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "16", "M": "46", "S": "07"}}, "news": [{"title": "Spain, Portugal step up scrutiny of soaring property markets", "para": "Spain and Portugal are closely watching their booming property markets, which show early signs of overheating with significant price hikes and strong mortgage lending. While regulators are introducing minor cooling measures, like adjusting debt-to-income ratios in Portugal, heavy intervention is unlikely. Current market conditions, though robust, are not mirroring the pre-2008 boom, with analysts suggesting supply constraints and a strong economy are driving current price growth.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/international/spain-and-portugal-monitor-surging-property-prices-amid-economic-growth/132216671?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-408418/132216671.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "international"}, {"title": "India office leasing hits 24.6 million sq ft in Q2 2026: Report", "para": "India\u2019s office market recorded gross leasing of about 24.6 million sq ft in Q2 2026, the highest quarterly absorption on record, according to CBRE. New completions stood at about 21 million sq ft during the quarter, while GCCs accounted for 42% of total office space take-up.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/commercial/india-office-leasing-reaches-record-246-million-sq-ft-in-q2-2026/132217223?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-1230873/132217223.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "commercial"}, {"title": "Rentomojo gets Sebi's approval to float IPO", "para": "Rentomojo, the online rental and subscription platform for furniture and appliances, has secured Sebi's approval for its Initial Public Offering (IPO). The company plans to raise Rs 150 crore through a fresh issue and an Offer for Sale by existing shareholders. Proceeds will fund loan repayments, warehouse leases, and general corporate needs.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/allied-industries/rentomojo-secures-sebi-approval-for-ipo-key-details-inside/132216597?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-23746/132216597.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "allied-industries"}]}